441
00:35:25,119 --> 00:35:29,899
♪People come and go,
the weather is ever-changing♪

442
00:35:30,699 --> 00:35:35,659
♪Endless expectations and reminiscing♪

443
00:35:35,899 --> 00:35:40,709
♪Having no say in one's will♪

444
00:35:40,819 --> 00:35:41,749
♪Oh♪

445
00:35:42,099 --> 00:35:44,249
♪On the same path♪

446
00:35:44,839 --> 00:35:47,249
♪With different burdens♪

447
00:35:47,339 --> 00:35:49,399
♪And different destinations♪

448
00:35:51,769 --> 00:35:52,829
♪Oh♪

449
00:35:53,069 --> 00:35:55,509
♪Different steps♪

450
00:35:55,839 --> 00:35:58,149
♪Pursuing the same goal♪

451
00:35:58,559 --> 00:36:01,529
♪With different sense of belonging♪

452
00:36:05,579 --> 00:36:08,219
♪Oh, I see the exit♪

453
00:36:08,609 --> 00:36:10,849
♪Hey, there's no end to this♪

454
00:36:10,999 --> 00:36:16,619
♪A soul that has found its home,
devoting everything to love♪

455
00:36:16,639 --> 00:36:19,269
♪Oh, reasons that can be articulated♪

456
00:36:19,379 --> 00:36:21,909
♪Hey, can't escape
from the ridiculousness♪

457
00:36:22,089 --> 00:36:29,949
♪Destiny is a maze where those inside
